OL,6,BCURRENT PRACTICE AND FUTURE PROSPECTS  
OL,7,BFOR LAND RESTORATION AND CONSERVATION  
OL,8,                           CJanuary 6-15
OL,10,GLand lies unused due to economic and   
OL,11,Gsocial development. This programme will
OL,12,Gaim to provide an understanding of the 
OL,13,Gprinciples and practices of restoring  
OL,14,Gland to its former productivity.       
OL,16, Contact: International Seminars on     
OL,17,          01865 316636 for details.     
