OL,5,BSPECIAL VOLUNTEER NEEDED  C    December
OL,6,B                                       
OL,7, Warwickshire Wildlife Trust is looking 
OL,8,Gfor a volunteer to help look after its 
OL,9,GNature Centre at Brandon March nature  
OL,10,GReserve, just outside Coventry.        
OL,12, The ideal candidate will be someone who
OL,13, enjoys being in the countryside and    
OL,14, meeting others who like to take        
OL,15, advantage of the 200 acres of lakes,   
OL,16, marshes and woodland.                  
OL,18, Details from Andy Tasker: 01203 302912.
